<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/31573708-a-philosophy-of-loneliness"><img alt="A Philosophy of Loneliness" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1476357924l/31573708._SY160_.jpg" />
